Gist simplicity makes blogging fun and liberating experience while GitHub platform affords a familiar and comfortable editing experience. We'll render and host a readable version of your post with metadata necessary for fancy preview when you share on social media like Twitter, Reddit, Telegram or Facebook. We'll update your timeline and generate RSS Atom feed of your hoots. No ads. No Facebook or Google tracking. Not Medium or Wordpress where you are the product. No timeline shenanigans. GitHoot is an elegant medium for a more civilized discourse. Create a GitHub gist and start blogging already.
